%md
### Data ingestion (HDFS)

%sh
# Ingest data SureChEMBL
SureChEMBL="surechembl_p0.0.sdf
surechembl_p0.1.sdf
surechembl_p0.10.sdf
surechembl_p0.11.sdf
surechembl_p0.12.sdf
surechembl_p0.13.sdf
surechembl_p0.2.sdf
surechembl_p0.3.sdf
surechembl_p0.4.sdf
surechembl_p0.5.sdf
surechembl_p0.6.sdf
surechembl_p0.7.sdf
surechembl_p0.8.sdf
surechembl_p0.9.sdf
surechembl_p1.0.sdf
surechembl_p1.1.sdf
"

hadoop fs -mkdir hdfs://spark-marco-master-000/surechembl
for filename in $SureChEMBL; do
    curl http://zinc.docking.org/db/byvendor/surechembl/$filename.gz | gunzip | hadoop fs -Ddfs.block.size=32M -put - hdfs://spark-marco-master-000/surechembl/$filename
done

%sh
# Ingest data AKSci
AKSci="aksci_p0.0.sdf
aksci_p1.0.sdf"

hadoop fs -mkdir hdfs://spark-marco-master-000/aksci
for filename in $AKSci; do
    curl http://zinc.docking.org/db/byvendor/aksci/$filename.gz | gunzip | hadoop fs -Ddfs.block.size=2509K -put - hdfs://spark-marco-master-000/aksci/$filename
done

%sh
# Persist aksci in cPouta
hadoop distcp hdfs://spark-marco-master-000/aksci swift://mare.cpouta/aksci
